    public interface IQualifiable
extends IClass
    The value of a qualifiable element may be further qualified by one or more qualifiers.

    Constraints:

    • Constraint AASd-119: If any Qualifier.getKind() value of getQualifiers() is equal to QualifierKind.TEMPLATE_QUALIFIER and the qualified element inherits from IHasKind then the qualified element shall be of kind Template (IHasKind.getKind() = ModellingKind.TEMPLATE).

      This constraint is checked at Submodel.
